      "body" : "Splitting the Core wallet and node to separate executables, communicating over RPC/P2P, is a very old idea. No one has ever implemented it yet, though, it's pretty hard to do in practice. Or at least a lot of work. I don't know of anyone that has concrete plans to do so.\r\n\r\nIf you need anything soon I'd also suggest looking at other thin client software for that.",
